<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateContainer.UnbindTexture" Title="UnbindTexture method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateContainer">IStateContainer</PageRef> ->
    UnbindTexture
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>UnbindTexture</TypeRef> method removes a previously defined binding to an <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.ITextureBuffer">ITextureBuffer</PageRef>
      object, whether that binding was established by the <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateContainer.BindTexture">BindTexture</PageRef>
      or the <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IStateContainer.BindTextureWithCombinedSampler">BindTextureWithCombinedSampler</PageRef>
      method.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void UnbindTexture(TextureId textureId);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="TextureId!cobalt.graphics.TextureId" Name="textureId">
          The <TypeRef>TextureId</TypeRef> of the named texture object to unbind
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
